the chrome browser has chrome os, firefox has webian. And now, opera has: Opera OS. Opera OS a lightning fast operating system based on slitaz 3.0, the smallest complete distro. Featuring opera, one of the fastest browsers available for linux, and flash player. And all that is packed into just 65 megabytes!  &lt;a href=&quot;
